headline: Think UPS Stock Is Expensive? These Charts Might Change Your Mind
summary: Trading on almost 18 times Wall Street estimates for earnings this year, and with a recent history of disappointing the market, United Parcel Service (NYSE: UPS) stock may seem expensive.  UPS earnings represent a tale of two halves in 2024.  The first-half adjusted operating profit declined by 30.3% compared to the first half of 2023.
